"{\"uid\": \"troyrecord.com-2024-07-27-simone-biles-will-serve-as-the-anchor-on-three-of-four-events-for-the-u-s-during-olympic-qualifying-2\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"E-Edition  Sign up for email newsletters    Sign up for email newsletters  E-Edition  PARIS (AP) -Simone Bileswill begin her quest for a second Olympic all-around title when she competes in all four events during qualifying on Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 93, \"end\": 95, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9980428046280666, \"rank\": 0.0019478245496935443, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, 2020 Olympic champion Sunisa Lee and 2020 Olympic silver medalist Jordan Chiles will compete on all four events in qualifying.\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 265, \"end\": 275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jade Carey, the 2020 Olympic champion on floor exercise, will compete on vault.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 370, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hezly Rivera, at 16 by far the youngest member of Team USA, will compete on balance beam and uneven bars.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9976241666985162, \"rank\": 0.0014660871512676456, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}, {\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.999813207831009, \"rank\": 0.00018658935107741635, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During qualifying, four members of each five-woman team will compete on each event, with teams dropping their lowest score.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top eight teams will advance to the team final on Tuesday night.\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles will serve as the anchor, or final competitor on balance beam, floor exercise and vault.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will go next-to-last for the U.S. on uneven bars,where she has submitted an original skillto the International Gymnastics Federation.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 947, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Gymnastics Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Biles successfully completes the maneuver during qualifying, it will be entered into the sport's Code of Points, where it will carry her name.\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old superstar already has five elements named for her in the code.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, the top 24 individual qualifiers in the all-around will move on to the all-around finals scheduled for Aug. 1, with the caveat that no team may have more than two gymnasts.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans are looking to return to the top of the podium after finishing second to Russia in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1399, \"end\": 1412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9999999999606644, \"rank\": 3.136418224403142e-11, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.750649882282539, \"rank\": 0.3115724434699616, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1496, \"end\": 1501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9938998453558633, \"rank\": 0.0060878023637750325, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 MediaNews Group\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1552,